thread.title: Vickey A.
thread.title_full: Vital Choice reviewed by Vickey A.

author: Vickey A.
title: Vickey A.
text:
My holistic practicioner recommended Vital Choice to me BY NAME - which impressed me from the start! Since then, I've purchased both salmon and halibut several times now - excellent quality!!!
I live in Virginia, and appreciate how the eco-friendly packaging keeps the food frozen since shipping is from WA, so no worries at all!
With my last order I tried the 'Seasoning Sampler' and will absolutely re-order.
